{"tid":1394883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online/斷尾道具篇 - 膠袋滑水梯，附錄各式噴壺介紹","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:44:07.000Z","uid":35776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d544b3e8d7fcb65bb5c3def38cd93748a2a077d8","tid":1394883,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"將膠袋剪開連成大幅膠布，鋪係需要封鎖嘅斜道或樓梯上，再加油加水，就變成有落無上嘅滑水梯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先準備若干厚身黑色大垃圾袋<br />\n<br />\n(商城:批發，各大超市及家品雜貨有售)<br />\n <br />\n按膠袋尺寸及所需長度 計算膠袋要排成矩陣 2x6,3x8等等<br />\n<br />\n將所有黑色垃圾膠袋左右剪開鋪平<br />\n然後以田字形黐電線膠布<br />\n<br />\n成功得到一塊大枱布後<br />\n用風琴形摺法 ☆(WWWW形摺疊),摺到容易攞嘅大細，就得到<br />\n注<br />\n★為左容易辨認，可以用鮮色電線膠布(紅藍) 分辨頭尾位置，方便使用<br />\n<br />\n★為方便展開使用，可在尾部預先增加重量，更快展開整張枱布<br />\n<br />\n★現場唔會夠時間整，請預先製作<br />\n★一大張太難使用可以製作較小尺寸分別使用"},{"pid":"71c924de0ccbe00e74e2e36307abeb8e3f528aa9","tid":1394883,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現場唔會夠時間整，請預先製作</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737ba8c628ab213d06a30287211ca925266536ec","tid":1394883,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c924de0ccbe00e74e2e36307abeb8e3f528aa9","tid":1394883,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現場唔會夠時間整，請預先製作</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:03:28.000Z","msg":"打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要整可以好快但未必好靚仔，都可以照用到<br />\n<br />\n要整得靚仔請預先製作"},{"pid":"9a4ddb6cf752c26a88367e4394fd438d287c4323","tid":1394883,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"附錄<br />\n<br />\n噴壺介紹<br />\n<br />\nA 淋花噴霧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/1092609575/TB2rhtmrcuYBuNkSmRyXXcA3pXa_!!1092609575.jpg_960x960q75.jpg_.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi1%2F1092609575%2FTB2rhtmrcuYBuNkSmRyXXcA3pXa_%21%211092609575.jpg_960x960q75.jpg_.webp&h=a4bc64f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n價格：$8 ~ $1x<br />\n用法：拉一下噴一下，越大力越快噴嘅水柱就越強<br />\n射程：&lt;3.5m<br />\n用途：公民噴霧/做百厭細路<br />\n★記得買水柱噴霧兩用個種<br />\n<br />\n以下三種全為手動加壓噴咀，可以一直射水<br />\n★記得打滿氣★！！！<br />\n<br />\nB 膠樽噴槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/2811653295/TB2DCwlahSYBuNjSsphXXbGvVXa_!!2811653295.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi1%2F2811653295%2FTB2DCwlahSYBuNjSsphXXbGvVXa_%21%212811653295.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp&h=e05b219f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VvzB-nc5Hog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVvzB-nc5Hog&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=79118f42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VvzB-nc5Hog</a><br />\n12蚊店有售 $12<br />\n用法：500ml 以上膠樽適用，手動打氣，可以一直射水<br />\n射程：&lt;5m, 感覺上A款射速更快<br />\n好處：容量大，擰落汽水樽救火效果應該唔差，可以事前準備多個裝滿水嘅膠樽一擰即用，汽水樽抗壓設計可以承受更強氣壓<br />\n用途：公民噴霧/做百厭細路/救火隊<br />\n<br />\nC 原裝噴壺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/690315933/O1CN014VAxei1thMNFBSuVq_!!690315933.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi3%2F690315933%2FO1CN014VAxei1thMNFBSuVq_%21%21690315933.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp&h=3687979e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oU26GgjMm1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoU26GgjMm1U&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=74f0e45e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oU26GgjMm1U</a>4:10左右<br />\n<br />\n價格：$3x～5x都見過，睇地區同鋪頭，容量要睇款<br />\n射程: 4~5m<br />\n好處: 因為係原裝壺，應該可以打氣打得更好，更實淨，但用完要refill，有youtube教學改裝噴泡沫<br />\n用途：同上<br />\n<br />\nD 農藥 3L~10L都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/1602131015/O1CN01OmoPWp1JMuVkUPvrh_!!1602131015.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi3%2F1602131015%2FO1CN01OmoPWp1JMuVkUPvrh_%21%211602131015.jpg_1200x1200q75.jpg_.webp&h=fc2e8054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n價格：斷估幾十，O寶可能好平<br />\n手提噴霧計係最大型，漁農署滅蚊都係靠佢！！！<br />\n多枝柄指向性提高，更易控制<br />\n射程應該5~6m<br />\n<br />\n★部份C，D款設有減壓閥，安全性更高"}]}